{"tid":244070,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"[他媽哥池Mix] 召集所有玩Sanrio版既巴絲入黎討論下","createTime":"2017-05-15T06:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T10:40:52.000Z","uid":2208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af52b9abf96efa21f399a6213267c849be843cbc","tid":244070,"uid":2208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/141508_f3e409663714b8a47e66bc038f1c0cb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F141508_f3e409663714b8a47e66bc038f1c0cb4.jpg&h=5708c357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/141509_f3e409663714b8a47e66bc038f1c0cb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F141509_f3e409663714b8a47e66bc038f1c0cb4.jpg&h=bf1f53f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/141510_d1931d79499fa7ef51e757f059575413.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F141510_d1931d79499fa7ef51e757f059575413.jpg&h=23c94ecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/141510_f7ccc498f3771ec1f06f14a467182451.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F141510_f7ccc498f3771ec1f06f14a467182451.jpg&h=7f63dd21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上官網有介紹到<br />\n<a href=\"http://tamagotch.channel.or.jp/tamagotchi/mix/catalog/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftamagotch.channel.or.jp%2Ftamagotchi%2Fmix%2Fcatalog%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=37af4dc3\" target=\"_blank\">http://tamagotch.channel.or.jp/tamagotchi/mix/catalog/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我見出面係有個他媽哥池post <br />\n開多個係想集中討論sanrio版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/144053_1096e402fbde0e0593d94261f4aaf711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F144053_1096e402fbde0e0593d94261f4aaf711.jpg&h=b3a0af89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我啱啱開始玩 見到twin star幾得意就同佢生左仔<br />\n點知個仔好樣衰 <br />\n得隻眼係遺傳左呀媽 <br />\n不敢想像下一代 一定好醜樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲mix到d更加醜樣既出黎？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f033024a07197fe4fbcca7a2357812daf2118a6a","tid":244070,"uid":2208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/145246_609d40b3f370ead9393b521c61e546ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F145246_609d40b3f370ead9393b521c61e546ef.jpg&h=88dee68f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/145247_609d40b3f370ead9393b521c61e546ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F145247_609d40b3f370ead9393b521c61e546ef.jpg&h=60c9762e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人會淘呢d套？ <br />\nIg 見到好多 以為要自己織 <br />\n上淘寶睇原來都係幾十蚊個 <br />\n仲有好多款 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9036ca7c471908d53313bbe4f3a00911cd688b6","tid":244070,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04dbb62b72c1e35db87bca9548ff6e2eb5bbd90","tid":244070,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8c16b95b1bc3114b66599909ec832bee085f81","tid":244070,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4a51222c6f75832cffca6624de72b38eec26e1","tid":244070,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8448add378030da1e33c788eb8a44a210d50de","tid":244070,"uid":41131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"啱啱訂咗，留個名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efa3099b354aa32b1d26cf8a4993fcf28521558","tid":244070,"uid":13491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T13:42:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱訂咗，留個名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊到訂？"},{"pid":"6094734c39dac2d3e8fa030f1e7d1692f6786b69","tid":244070,"uid":2208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱訂咗，留個名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  終於有人玩啦陰公 <br />\n幾時到呀"},{"pid":"ef535feb09a7cb146748dacc20c446b366391149","tid":244070,"uid":2208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱訂咗，留個名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊到訂？</blockquote><br />\nIg search #他媽哥池 會搵到好多代購 <br />\n不過而家好多都要540 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9602a92a1eac64290c1270b2803bdeddc6c2a4df","tid":244070,"uid":41131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:00:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱訂咗，留個名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊到訂？</blockquote><br />\n我見ig無現貨就去咗淘寶買呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貪佢送埋mon貼攻略同會幫手刷機 <br />\n有無人試過hand carry上飛機？"},{"pid":"c8734dafbd4256cc51ef825b343c6a8a5ff218d9","tid":244070,"uid":34523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26ieTbn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26ieTbn.jpg&h=2be95749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問大家我應該買邊隻好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女朋友生日，我想買兩隻做禮物<br />\n但佢鍾意xo又未出"},{"pid":"47cc73bcb3562cb47059c00e271a2ac324383ec1","tid":244070,"uid":34523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:12:39.000Z","msg":"取向：<br />\n$540：2019年花紋無咁多心，同最新款<br />\n$400：2018年但唔知咩mix meet分別同太多心心我作為傳統男人有啲難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n$495：2017年始終女友起碼識sanrio，但遲啲出新。可惜新嗰部又唔知幾時先有正常價買到...."},{"pid":"f861abe25c53d75307ddd102d87127532eb01a5f","tid":244070,"uid":178684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:30:01.000Z","msg":"買咗新出個部Sanrio但發現身邊無朋友玩好難玩<br />\n起碼要兩部係身"},{"pid":"932b0b3bb11ec73cccae6deee4784a83e79936f0","tid":244070,"uid":7204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"有冇人知佢發生咩事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yVVhJqx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyVVhJqx.png&h=edd15a24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51c5503be86351e51648a10f752f059eeebff4f7","tid":244070,"uid":178684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"932b0b3bb11ec73cccae6deee4784a83e79936f0","tid":244070,"uid":7204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"有冇人知佢發生咩事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yVVhJqx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyVVhJqx.png&h=edd15a24&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:40:52.000Z","msg":"無電啊 換電！"}]}